getInheritParentRelationships

public boolean getInheritParentRelationships()
Returns whether to inherit parent relationships when creating a new revision. If this flag is set to true, new revisions of the child item will inherit all the parent relationships associated with the base revision it is being created from.

Returns:
true/false

getInheritChildRelationships

public boolean getInheritChildRelationships()
Returns whether to inherit child relationships when creating a new revision. If this flag is set to true, new revisions of the parent item will inherit all the child relationships associated with the base revision it is being created from.

Returns:
true/false
